files.text: It appears, due to circumstances entirely out of my control, that despite every best effort I am forced to draw the conclusion from matters entirely separate from your actions that all fucks which were previously reserved here for your convenience have now found themselves within something of a deficit.
files.name: out-of-control

files.text: I've checked my **things to do** list. I searched a lot but giving a fuck about you just isn't there
files.name: things-to-do-list

files.text: **NASA** sent a deep space probe to the planet `Giveafuckaboutyou` and confirmed that I wasn't there
files.name: nasa-space-probe

files.text: Your web search **times I give a fuck about you** returned no results. Did you mean **times I don't give a fuck about you?**
files.name: web-search

files.text: Today's lesson is titled **I don't give a fuck about you**. Tomorrow's lesson is the same as today's!!
files.name: lesson-todays

files.text: **Wanting** you to fuck off and **giving** a fuck about you are not the same thing. So fuck off!!
files.name: deep-meanings
